                                patient last urinated</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Topic:</entry>
                            <entry><para>Measurement-of Systolic blood pressure</para><para><emphasis role="bold"
                                        >Approach/Access Route:</emphasis> Right brachial artery
                                    (technique)</para><para><emphasis role="bold">Body
                                        Position:</emphasis> Seated (technique)</para></entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Subject of information:</entry>
                            <entry>Subject of record</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Statement time:</entry>
                            <entry/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>Act:</entry>
                            <entrytbl cols="3">
                                <colspec colnum="1" colname="c1" colwidth="1.86*"/>
